5851a861bce12.Name: List Office Locations
5851a861bce12.Output_template:
{"lookup_validation":"0","systemID":"57b1c45c19a40","systemName":"FirmStep Lookups","query":"SELECT TOP (1000) ol.[id] as name
      ,[companyName]
      ,[longCompanyName]
      ,[displayCompanyName] as display
      ,[utcOffset]
      ,[addressLine1]
      ,[addressLine2]
      ,[townCity]
      ,[region]
      ,[countryDisplay]
      ,[countryID]
      ,[postCode]
      ,[phoneNumber]
      ,[CASReporting]
      ,[LIM]
      ,[lat]
      ,[lng]
      ,ol.[archived]
		,a.group_id as admin_group
		,m.group_id as manager_group
		,d.group_id as director_group
  FROM [FirmstepLookupsDev].[dbo].[OfficeLocation] ol
	left join (OfficeLocationRole a inner join role ar on a.role_id=ar.id) on ol.id=a.office_location_id and ar.name = 'ERROL Admin'
	left join (OfficeLocationRole m inner join role mr on m.role_id=mr.id) on ol.id=m.office_location_id and mr.name = 'ERROL Manager'
	left join (OfficeLocationRole d inner join role dr on d.role_id=dr.id) on ol.id=d.office_location_id and dr.name = 'ERROL Director'
	where ol.archived=0
	order by displayCompanyName","results_page_columns_db":"","secure_fields_db_database":"","escapeTokens":"yes"}
